1 (15) Violation of § 10–604, § 10–605, § 10–606, § 10–607, § 10–607.1, or §
2 10–608 of the Criminal Law Article, whether a felony or misdemeanor;
3 (16) Violation of Title 7, Subtitle 3, Part III of the Criminal Law Article,
4 whether a felony or misdemeanor;
5 (17) Violation of § 20–102 of the Transportation Article, whether a felony or
6 misdemeanor;
7 (18) Violation of § 8–801 of the Criminal Law Article;
8 (19) Violation of § 8–604 of the Criminal Law Article;
